{{Update|inaccurate=yes|the current name of the merged magazine; the publisher has created a new online portal around 2012 named Institutional Investor's Alpha; website www.absolutereturn-alpha.com redirects to www.institutionalinvestorsalpha.com|date=January 2014}} {{Infobox Magazine |title = AR: Absolute Return + Alpha |image_file =Absolute Return + Alpha cover.jpg |image_size =180px |editor = Michael Peltz |editor_title = Editor |frequency = Web: Daily / Print: Monthly |circulation = 9,000 |category = Business and management magazine |publisher = [[Euromoney Institutional Investor]] |founded = 2009 |firstdate = |country = United States |based= [[New York City]] |language = [[English language|English]] |website = [http://www.absolutereturn-alpha.com www.absolutereturn-alpha.com] |issn = 2151-1837 }}
'''''AR: Absolute Return + Alpha''''' (or '''''AR''''') is a hedge fund magazine founded in 2009. The magazine has its editorial offices in New York City.<ref name=fwpr/>
==History and profile== ''Absolute Return + Alpha'' (''AR'') was launched in September 2009, as a subsidiary of financial publisher [[Euromoney Institutional Investor]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Euromoney Institutional Investor PLC Launches a New Hedge Fund|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=alxJwGBu80c0|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208175145/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=alxJwGBu80c0|dead-url=yes|archive-date=8 December 2015|accessdate=5 December 2015|work=Bloomberg Business|date=9 September 2009}} </ref> ''AR'' was formed when two magazines, ''Alpha'' and ''Absolute Return'', were combined.<ref name=fwpr>{{cite news|author=Frank Washkuch|title='Alpha' and 'Absolute Return' to merge into 'AR' for September launch|url=http://www.prweek.com/article/1271287/alpha-absolute-return-merge-ar-september-launch|accessdate=5 December 2015|work=PR Week|date=22 June 2009}}</ref> The magazine publishes both online and print content. Its main focus is the hedge fund industry and its 3,500 fund managers, but the magazine also covers significant financial events and global research. The magazine features hedge fund rankings according to [[assets under management]] rankings, an annual ranking of the 25 highest paid hedge fund managers, and monthly tables of U.S. hedge fund performance data.<ref>[http://www.absolutereturn-alpha.com/AboutUs.html Official Web Site] About Us, Retrieved Oct 2011</ref>
