[[File:CQ Science Museum.JPG|thumb|The [[Chongqing Science & Technology Museum]] in Jiangbeizui CBD.]]
'''Jiangbeizui CBD''' ([[Central Business District]]) is a part of [[Liangjiang New Area]] in central [[Chongqing]], [[China]].
<!-- The CBD covers an area of 50,000 km<sup>2</sup>. --> The CBD aims to attract financial institutions, making it a [[financial center]] in the future.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://english.liangjiang.gov.cn/2014-01/07/content_17229036.htm | title=Jiangbeizui Financial Center | publisher=[http://english.liangjiang.gov.cn/ Chongqing Liangjiang New Area] | location=China | date=7 January 2014 | accessdate=23 August 2014 }}</ref> It is expected to be completed in 2018.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://en.cq.gov.cn/ChongqingToday/News/3998.htm | title=Chongqing Jiangbeizui CBD takes shape and is expected to be fully completed by 2018 | publisher=[[Chongqing Municipal Government]] | date=17 June 2013 | accessdate=23 August 2014 }}</ref>
Jiangbeizui CBD is located by the [[Yangtze River]], near the confluence with the [[Jialing River]] immediately across Chongqing city's primary downtown hub of [[Jeifangbei CBD]]. The world class [[Chongqing Science and Technology Museum]] is located here.
